reviewText: The item took a while to get, but was in excellent shape.  Unfortunately, Mike Marino rehashes the same routines and just is not that funny any more.  I would recommend the seller, but not the item.
The video doesnt do justice to the comedian, it was poorly produced and edited and looks more like a home video. It's a real shame because the comedian is hysterical and very talented.

Mike Marino - Live From Los Angeles I saw a funny utube video of his and decided to order his dvd. I was terribly disappointed. The video was poor and every other word out of his mouth was the "F" or "MF" word. It was not funny, it was appalling.
